title: Los Angeles/West
name: Tacos A La Flama
directions: Olympic Blvd and Bundy Dr, in strip mall next to Subway and Leeds Mattresse
content: Mexican taco stand offering tacos, burritos, sopes and the like. Adventurous eaters can try tacos de lengua (beef tongue), cabeza (beef cheek), tripa (tripe) and buche (beef esophagus).
